Thank you Jose!!! These cookies are beyond belief. I make them about once a month and bring them to the office and they're GONE within two hours. I'm now famous for these cookies. Don't change a thing in the recipe -- remember to chill them long enough. One time I was in a hurry and didn't and they came out crunchy instead of that wonderful chewy texture, but they were still good. These are the cookies I make when I want to impress someone or give a "thank you" gift.

