Rating: 4
I too am ever on the search for that perfect chocolate/peanut butter combination and this is as good as it gets in terms of cookies. These are great! I used quick oats and still got a great texture (and saved some hassle). I thought the 8 oz. of ground chocolate overrode the peanut butter taste slightly, so next time I'll probably use lest chocolate (and sub some milk chocolate) and use a little more peanut butter. I underbaked mine a little (12 minutes) and got a nice gooey middle and softness that lasted for a few days. This is my new cookie recipe!

