This is my new favorite cookie recipe .. with a few modifications. I used quick oats and didn't grind them. Instead of chocolate chips/grated chocolate, I used a mixture of milk and dark chocolate baking discs (about the size of a quarter) and pressed them into the cookies just before baking. They are amazing! I refrigerated the dough overnight and had to bake them this morning since I couldn't wait to try them.

